A practical guide to BitBake tutorial: by Harald Achitz
Version 1.6,  2022 Q2

https://a4z.gitlab.io/docs/BitBake/guide.html



Bitbake Source code sync:

git clone -b 1.52.0 https://github.com/openembedded/bitbake


#Add bitbake binary and pythonpath, as done by yocto init script.
export PATH=$PWD/bitbake/bin:$PATH
export PYTHONPATH=$PWD/bitbake/lib:$PYTHONPATH

Or alternatively you can run environment setup script.


#Check verisions for compatibility match
Run python3 --version to check version of python is 3.8.8 or later 
Run bibake --version to check the version of bitbake is 1.52.0




